+# Platform HAL stack (camera.msm8937.so, mm-qcamera-daemon, libmmcamera2_*,
+# ISP modules, etc.) is pulled from montana via camera-vendor.mk — do not
+# list those here. XT1765 stock sensors are imx219 / s5k4h8 / mot_ov5695
+# (see configs/camera/msm8917_mot_perry_camera.xml); chromatix/sensor libs
+# below still need a stock rewrite (many montana leftovers).
